Package: microspectr
Title: Process raw data from clariostar spectrophotometer
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Yoann", "Anciaux", , "anciaux.yoann@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2845-4034"))
Description: A toolbox to 'tidy' raw signal data from the BMG clariostar spectrophotometer. You provide the data, tell 'microspectr' what signal and how it should analyse it and it take care of the details.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
